title: Volcom - BEAST MODE - Zeke Lau
description:
On Decemeber 1st 2013, Zeke Lau won the Van's World Cup of Surfing at Sunset Beach. This is a video documenting Zeke from the Quarters on to him winning the the World Cup of Surfing.


Thank You to Vans & Uncle Toads Media Group for providing us with the majority of the footage to make this piece.
